    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, boil half a kettle and take your <strong>chicken </strong>out of the fridge, open the packet and let it air</p><p>Peel and finely slice your <strong>red onion[s]</strong></p><p>Peel and chop your <strong>sweet potato[es]</strong> into bite-sized pieces</p><p>Trim, then chop your <strong>green beans</strong> in half</p><p>Crush your <strong>cardamom</strong> <strong>pod[s]</strong> open by squashing them with the side of a knife</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Chopped-chicken-thigh---browned-1683881826421-x200.jpg",
