            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Return the pan to a medium-high heat with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong></p><p>Once hot, add your <strong>diced chicken thigh </strong>and<strong> sliced onion</strong> with a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and <strong>pepper</strong> and cook for an initial 4-5 min or until the chicken is starting to brown</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/R1305tep-3-x200.jpg",
