          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once starting to brown, add your <strong>ground coriander</strong>, <strong>crushed cardamom pod[s]</strong> and <strong>red Thai curry paste </strong>to the pan and cook for 1-2 min further or until the chicken is coated in the spices</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
