            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>coconut stock, chopped sweet potato </strong>and<strong> lime leaf[ves] </strong>to the pan and cook, covered, for 8-10 min until the sweet potato is almost fork-tender</p><p>Once fork-tender, add the <strong>halved green beans </strong>with a pinch of<strong> salt</strong> and cook for a further 3-4 min further or until the beans are tender and the chicken is cooked through (no pink meat!) – this is your <strong>massaman-style chicken curry</strong></p>",
      "order": 7,
