      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Discard the <strong>cardamom</strong> <strong>pod[s]</strong> and<strong> lime</strong> <strong>leaf[ves] </strong>from the curry</p><p>Serve the <strong>massaman-style chicken curry </strong>with the <strong>cooked rice</strong> to the side</p><p>Garnish with the <strong>toasted cashews</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
